&lt;li&gt;Ongoing review of business reports and participation in regular business reviews with international sales leadership to build a deep understanding of the business and identify opportunities to improve sales operational excellence. Act as a point person for operational questions, issues, and ideation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally to lead new sales programs or process rollouts and execute sales operations requirements. Assess program risks &amp;amp; provide options for mitigation. Utilise project management tools to remain organized and communicate program updates to stakeholders regularly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver best-in-class sales training for our 3P partner(s) sales teams. Support training and sales capabilities of 3P at store level&lt;/li&gt;
