&lt;li&gt;Analyse operational data from a Sales Operations lens to identify trends, track performance, and generate reports, on a monthly and quarterly basis to inform decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively communicate with cross-functional teams and stakeholders, both internally and externally, ultimately building strong relationships and fostering collaboration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
