&lt;li&gt;Correspond with NY and Seattle based team with test reports and status updates , which will require morning/evening calls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with technicians for various testing activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively perform preliminary root cause/failure analysis to collaborate with &amp;amp; drive cross functional team to resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Validation lead to utilize statistical tools to compile the result into impact to real world application&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work multi-functionally with other departments and capture the specific scope of request&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Standardize test documentation, including fixtures, test procedures, schematics and software program. Supervise and implement test processes and data flow&lt;/li&gt;
